program.tc:
Keyword buying policy 
Buongiorno allows affiliates to: 
- link directly to their own website/landing page; 
- buy keywords at Google on the CONTENT network only;
- buy keywords at Yahoo and other sponsored links, on both SEARCH and CONTENT networks;
- optimize their website in order to improve their position in natural search results;
Do not promote any of the Blinko campaigns and creatives on website uploading.com. and Uploadbox.com

Buongiorno does not allow partners to: 
- buy keywords at Google on the SEARCH network; 
- buy keywords at Google, Yahoo and other sponsored links where search words are used that are copyright protected;
- buy keywords with the brand names 'buongiorno' and/or 'buon giorno', 'blinko', 'blinkotones', 'blinko tones' and/or 'blinko club';
- outbid Buongiorno in all sponsored links; 
- link directly (or a redirect) to Buongiorno, no matter what keyword is used;
- link directly with a partner-tracking link; 
- use the name Buongiorno e/o ‘Blinko’ in the description; 
- use the name Buongiorno e/o ‘Blinko’ in the Display URL.
-use the word ‘gratis’ or ‘free’, or misleading terms in the description or in the display URL

